text: Maha Amer (born 27 March 1999) is an Egyptian diver. She competed in the women's three metre springboard event at the 2016 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Egyptian female divers Category:Olympic divers of Egypt Category:Divers at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
